retweeted_text: .@RepRashida, @RepDanKildee, @RepSlotkin, @RepCicilline, & @RepGwenMoore have introduced a crucial amendment to the #MovingForward Act to #ProtectCleanWater & #GetTheLeadOut of service lines. This would protect communities' health, create jobs, & more than pay for itself!

full_text: Our local communities are on the fronline of stopping the spread of #COVID19—but they were already struggling before this pandemic. It’s time to grant them adequate relief aid. Read about this much-needed bill—cosponsored by 14 of our colleagues—here: https://t.co/2g5IiRySjg.

With first individual in our federal prison system testing positive for #COVID19 at #MDCBrooklyn I joined today with @RepAOC @RepPressley @RepRashida to call for compassionate release of those who are elderly or have health conditions & present no public safety risk. 
Read more: https://t.co/m31J16Q2sT

full_text: I fully support the @FSCDems #COVID19 economic response proposal. I also want to encourage leadership to consider my truly universal relief proposal on behalf of #13thDistrictStrong.

full_text: WATCH: Recently, I went to the House floor to remember Mama Lila Cabbil. • Allow harmful work requirements

Every time Trump talks about this "crisis," I ask: How can this be a "crisis" when he had a GOP House and Senate for TWO YEARS, and there was no crisis then? He could not get his own party to fund this "crisis."

And now that Dems control the House, it's a "crisis."

full_text: America cannot wait. We need to pass #HR8 and bring about bipartisan solutions to tackle gun violence. Background checks on gun sales & transfers is the most effective & efficient way to start saving lives. We need to pass #HR8 immediately! #NeverAgain
